  "body": "<img alt=\"22a-DSC_1296-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bed3215e6b44f61a.jpg?v=1782536753\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"22b-DSC_1295-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a9973f911f0bcd64.jpg?v=1782536756\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22c-DSC_1297-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9f6401e6c9f30877.jpg?v=1782536759\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22d-DSC_1299-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a978593931e90127.jpg?v=1782536762\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22e-DSC_1303-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/83679b4fe5d1cbcf.jpg?v=1782536764\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22f-DSC_1304-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a3c0a5dde02b069b.jpg?v=1782536767\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/silhouette-cameo-machine/silhouette-cameo?aff=6cc2c70f\">Silhouette</a> got a lot of use this month. The <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1awBDfK\">digital cut files</a> are out of this world and so easy to use. </p><p>I could have easily made a dozen layouts with the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/roundabout?aff=6cc2c70f\">Roundabout kits</a> from Studio Calico, but I was out of town for much of May. Actually, I spent every single weekend away from home. One of them was at Camp Calico, where I made <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/89994-hello-melbourne?aff=6cc2c70f\">this layout</a>. You can see all 8 of my projects in the gallery <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/roundabout/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">here</a>.</p>"
